data.description: Charming Corner Lot Home with Pool and Breezeway located behind St. Agnes Hospital in Fresno, CA. Welcome to your opportunity to own a spacious 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home with a refreshing pool and a delightful breezeway tile roof and custom closets. This 1,860 square foot home is situated on a generous 8200 sq ft corner lot in a desirable neighborhood. While it may need a bit of updating, it's brimming with potential and is a perfect canvas for those looking to make it their own. In addition to all-new ceiling fans, the kitchen is equipped with new faucets, a disposal, dishwasher, microwave, and range. The air conditioning has been regularly maintained to ensure your comfort year-round. Cozy up in the spacious living area with a gas starter fireplace..
